{"tid":248431,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲開設航空公司","createTime":"2017-05-18T14:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T14:38:09.000Z","uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04c12e0e4c7729bcbb38e9ccc9ad1ee9fceef5c8","tid":248431,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"復興航空（簡稱復航、興航[1] ）是中華民國第一家民營航空公司，創立於1951年5月21日，1983年由國產實業集團接手經營。主要經營國內航線以及區域國際航線。樞紐機場在臺灣桃園國際機場及臺北松山機場，提供客運和地勤代理的服務。曾經於2014年成立經營低成本航空子公司威航。"},{"pid":"bdd7a1908ae0bb707d0a6932ac447428d7cee838","tid":248431,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"云伯係咪有個「復興電台」？<br />\n<br />\n但我搵唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf7d013029917a51577d2713be0098171f99cbe","tid":248431,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>云伯係咪有個「復興電台」？<br />\n<br />\n但我搵唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毓民叫佢開<br />\n但不才查兩查<br />\n原來國師係航空大亨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/222952_e98786f06c4cefdb575434e38d9591bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F222952_e98786f06c4cefdb575434e38d9591bd.jpg&h=bcd349f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f709be80c4a639e733ffa236ecc677820872d15","tid":248431,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.hkpeanut.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/%E6%96%87%E5%8F%88%E5%94%94%E6%96%87%E5%BE%97-1024x536.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.hkpeanut.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F03%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258F%2588%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25BE%2597-1024x536.png&h=b1c3540a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f99a79221fcdb9d927c6df9f00ab01061eb100","tid":248431,"uid":389,"like